            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Refreshing the filters releases absorbed odor molecules from the filters, renewing them to near their original absorbing ability. To refresh your bag: Turn the bag inside-out. Place the bag in the dryer on low for a few minutes or until warm. OR place it outside in the sun for a few hours or until warm.</p>",
